<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <title>{% block title %}Welcome!{% endblock %}</title>
    {% block stylesheets %}{% endblock %}
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/vendor/foundation-sites/dist/foundation.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/foundation-icons/foundation-icons.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/pascalvervest.css">

    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="{{ asset('favicon.ico') }}" />
</head>
<body>
    <div class="callout large primary">
        <div class="row column text-center">
            <h1>pascalvervest.nl</h1>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row homeContent">
        <div class="medium-6 columns medium-push-6">
            <img class="thumbnail" src="http://placehold.it/750x350">
        </div>
        <div class="medium-6 columns medium-pull-6">
            <h2>Oh hai!</h2>
            <p>Welcome to my little place on the interwebz! This site is mainly used as an online portfolio, and to play around with some new technologies. (Did I mention that this is build on the awesome <a target="_BLANK" href="https://symfony.com/">Symfony3</a> framework?)</p>
            <p><small>And no, this thing is far from done, as is of course, tradition</small></p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row homeContent">
        <div class="medium-4 columns">
            <h3>Web development</h3>
            <p>Random stuff about my ventures into web/software development.</p>
            <a class="readMore" href="#">read more...</a>
        </div>
        <div class="medium-4 columns">
            <h3>Music</h3>
            <p>I like music. A lot! I'm active in several bands, and do other stuff as well!</p>
            <a class="readMore" href="#">read more...</a>
        </div>
        <div class="medium-4 columns">
            <h3>Gaming</h3>
            <p>If I'm not working, or doing something music-related, I spend a lot of times playing games, ranging from RPG's to simulations.</p>
            <a class="readMore" href="#">read more...</a>
        </div>
    </div>

{% block body %}{% endblock %}
{% block javascripts %}{% endblock %}
</body>
</html>
